snapshot:
Mr Infinity Services



Web Design

I offer design for your services on Tor. I can design everything myself or act as a consultant to help you make your service look good. No prepayments required for this service but I need spare time.

Managed Shops

For those of you who just want start business on Tor without worrying about the technical side I can provide a managed service. This includes your shop being set up and hosted securely.

Paypal Accounts

I offer paypal accounts. These accounts are hacked. All accounts have a guaranteed balance of $300 on them. Not a product for people who don't know how to cash them out. No guidance provided.

Hacking Services

I reluctantly list my hacking services here. Occasionally I may take an interesting job. Please do not contact me about a job that is boring or which you could do yourself after an hour of reading.

If you are looking for any of the above services I may be able help. I have a lot of experience and am sensitive to the privacy needs of clients.

The cost of web design is determined per hour and depends on what you need done. The price will be reasonable. You get to see the finished product before you pay. I will ask for proof that you have the required funds before beginning work on your project. This service depends on me having the time to design things.

Managed sites and stores will be set up and hosted for you. You still need to write your own content. You can view the product before making payment. The cost for a basic package is a $30 set-up fee and then $5 (or $2.50!) a month for hosting and management. I will ask for proof that you have the required funds before beginning work on your site. You do not need to write any code.

I offer paypal accounts for cashing out. You need to know how to cash them out. No support will be provided after purchase and if you get the account flagged no refund is provided. There are plenty of guides on the deepweb for this. The starting price is $90. Payment is made before I provide the credentials. House rule: Anyone who buys 2 accounts gets a third free. Third account will have a random balance.

I will rarely accept hacking projects. This is because I do not want to draw attention to myself or my service, and also because they can be hard. Price and payment depends on what is being done.

Special Offers!

Hidden Answers special offer: I am currently advertising on Hidden Answers, a deepweb forum. Verified members of Hidden Answers will get a 10% discount on any PayPal account they purchase. Verified members are those with at least 1 question. Please mention this in your order and provide proof that you own an account.
This offer will end: July/5.

Hidden Answers special offer: Verified Hidden Answers users who decide to open a managed store with us will have the option of a second managed store free-of-charge.

Buy 2 paypals, get a third free.
This offer will end: Never.

Allow a small banner on your managed store linking back to this site and get 50% off your hosting costs.
This offer will end: Never.
